channel.title: How To Change Home Tele PLEASE
channel.description: Ok. My home tele is in the Varrock slot.. I just want to change the coords.. Unfortunately, when the home tele was coded, it was make as a.. "toX:" "toY:" and not just like a normal coord tele.. So idk what the coords are to and from, and idk how to find em and change it.. I have a new home completed, I just need my tele complete..

item.title: How To Change Home Tele PLEASE
item.dc:creator: @FuryofEdge FuryofEdge
item.description:
@FuryofEdge wrote:

case 73148:
case 4146:
c.triggerTele(2870, 3589, 0);
break;
case 50253:
c.triggerTele(2870, 3589, 0);
break;
case 73136:
case 4143:
case 50245: // edgeville teleport
c.teleEffect = 1;
c.sendQuest(“Which wild zone?”, 2470);
c.sendQuest(“Edgeville”, 2471);
c.sendQuest(“Varrock”, 2472);
c.sendQuest(“Mage bank”, 2473);
c.sendFrame164(2469);
break;

thats what i get in the clicking most, and theres only a couple teles. u can see what is what, but the top like 2-3 arent noted, so idk wtf they are so how do i find out… the home tele is the very first tele in the mage book, but idk which 1 it would be above “edgeville teleport” but in the mage book in game, theres only 1 tele before that edgeville teleport, which is home tele… not like 2-3. so…[br][br][size=1]Posted on: August 12, 2009, 06:39:47 pm[/size][hr]can u help me out plz?
